Bharti, Idea, Vodafone Close to Signing 3G Agreement, WSJ Says

-- B y   H a r i   G o v i n d
-- 
2011-03-28T06:00:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/bharti-idea-vodafone-close-to-signing-3g-agreement-wsj-says.html
Bharti Airtel Ltd. (BHARTI) , Vodafone Essar
Ltd. and  Idea Cellular Ltd. (IDEA)  are close to signing an agreement to
share their third-generation radio bandwidth, the Wall Street
Journal reported on its website today, without saying where it
got the information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Hari Govind at 
 hgovind@bloomberg.net  